# VHS tape for the README demo GIF.
# Regenerate with: VHS_NO_SANDBOX=true vhs demo.tape   (run from inside assets/demo/teach-me/)
# Requires: https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs (and ffmpeg + ttyd)

Output demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000
Set Height 560
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Hide
Type "clear && bash repl.sh"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "teach me Python decorators"
Sleep 600ms
Enter

Sleep 26s
